title: CGI Star Professional 5.19 [Full]
description:
Automatically creates and installs CGIs for Web forms. Lets you
receive a form input as text/HTML e-mail or the entire form as
it appears on the Web. Attach and send local files from user&#039;s
PC. Format the mail in any way you like. Wizard-style interface
to set up and go in a few minutes. Immediate setup, unlimited
number of form elements, many customizable options, improved
stability, and a host of form templates. CGI on your server or
on ours.

Version 5.19 may include unspecified updates, enhancements, or
bug fixes.
